  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Self-catering apartments in the centre of Äkäslompolo within walking distance of the local supermarket. All apartments are equipped with a small kitchenette, giving you the option to dine in or check out the local restaurants in the village.</p>
<p>Optional supplement for half <span>board includes a breakfast buffet and an evening dinner buffet with three courses; the menu features Lappish specialties and locally sourced products. Meals are taken</span><span> at the Äkäs Hotel which is around 100 metres away from the apartments.</span></p>
<p>There is an optional credit (approx. €10 adult &amp; €5 child) towards the à la carte menu instead of buffet dinner. Please inform the hotel reception by 6pm the night before.</p>
<p>New Year's Eve gala dinner, live music and dance included for guests pre-booking half board. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
