  <description><![CDATA[<p>The highly recommended Äkäs Alp Apartments are situated in the traditional unspoilt Lappish community of Äkäslompolo in a scenic and peaceful wooded location in the <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas"><span>Ylläs</span></a> area. </p>
<h2>Relaxation at its finest</h2>
<p>The comfortable apartments are in the most convenient location for reaching the centre of Äkäslompolo village and you'll be able to make the most of the facilities at the nearby Äkäs Hotel. Have a dip in the indoor pool, or unwind and rejuvenate in your own private sauna- excellent for warming up after a day of exploration.</p>
<h2>Self-catered apartments with half board upgrade option</h2>
<p>Our self-catered apartments are designed to be your cosy home away from home. They all have a kitchenette and cooking facilities (hob and microwave) so you'll have the choice to eat in or try out some of the local spots - restaurants, bars, and a well-stocked supermarket are just a walk away. And if you'd prefer tasty meals without any fuss, our optional half board upgrade to the nearby Äkäs Hotel (approx. 100 metres), means you can focus all of your attention on days spent exploring <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">Lapland</a>.</p>
<h2>Your gateway to Lapland adventures</h2>
<p>You'll be within walking distance of the meet point for many of our pre-bookable excursions and activities and the ski bus stop just outside the Äkäs Hotel. So you can spend your days gliding down the slopes, snowmobiling through the arctic landscape or on a husky or reindeer safari.</p>
<p>With a convenient 5-10 minute walk (500 meters), you'll find yourself in the village centre. Immerse yourself in the local culture and explore the hidden treasures of Äkäslompolo.</p>]]></description>
